overview.en: Turing private fund raising exclusive token. AI assisted quantitative trading fund. Low risk and robust strategy, expected annualized income of more than 100%. Limited sales, only Tik fundraising. 80% of the fund income is used to buy back Tik and distribute dividends to fund investors.
